org.jpasecurity.collection

Class AbstractSecureCollection<E,T extends Collection<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • org.jpasecurity.collection.AbstractSecureCollection<E,T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultSecureCollection, SecureSet, SecureSortedSet

    public abstract class AbstractSecureCollection<E,T extends Collection<E>>
extends AbstractCollection<E>
    This is the base class for secure collections. Secure collections filter collections based on the accessibility of their elements.

    Arne Limburg
